---
title: British Pork Pie with Green Peas and Apple Chutney
description: The humble British pork pie is a thing of beauty. Creamy peas, crisp buttery flakey pastry, and tender pork. A dollop of sweet sticky apple chutney brings this whole dish to its British glory!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tourte-au-porc-a-langlaise-6ac76a5d.jpg
